RICHMOND COUNCIL ASK FOR MORE FOR POLICE
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    The Council was unanimous last week in its criticism of the
    Government and Mayor of London for underfunding local policing.

    At the full Council meeting, members from across the political
    divide called on the Government and the Mayor of London to
    recognise the valid concerns of local people and businesses about
    an increase of some of the most violent crimes in the borough.

