STEP UP AND TAKE PART IN RICHDANCE 2019
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    The RichDance Festival, Richmond upon Thames' annual showcase
    for new dance, is back and looking for the fleet footed to float
    across the 2019 stage.

    The Festival is returning for a seventeenth year and is open to all
    dance groups and all forms of dance. Over 600 people secured
    tickets to last year's festival.

